description: With Meal Ideas, Alexa will help you figure out what to make for your next meal. Simply ask Alexa to start Meal Ideas and Alexa will give you some meal options. This skill is helpful for those times when you just can't think of something to make.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask meal ideas to tell me a meal idea.
Alexa, ask meal ideas to tell me something.
name: Meal Ideas
shortDescription: Can't think of something to make for your next meal? Ask Alexa for some options.
